Moves.Name: Absorb
Moves.Description: An attack that absorbs half the damage it inflicted to restore HP.

Moves.Name: Acid
Moves.Description: The foe is sprayed with a harsh, hide-melting acid that may lower DEFENSE.

Moves.Name: Acid Armor
Moves.Description: The user alters its cells to liquefy itself and sharply raise DEFENSE.

Moves.Name: Aerial Ace
Moves.Description: An extremely fast attack against one target. It can’t be evaded.

Moves.Name: Aeroblast
Moves.Description: A vortex of air is shot at the foe. It has a high critical-hit ratio.

Moves.Name: Agility
Moves.Description: The user relaxes and lightens its body to sharply boost its SPEED.

Moves.Name: Air Cutter
Moves.Description: The foe is hit with razor-like wind. It has a high critical-hit ratio.

Moves.Name: Amnesia
Moves.Description: Forgets about something and sharply raises SP. DEF.

Moves.Name: Ancientpower
Moves.Description: An ancient power is used to attack. It may also raise all the user’s stats.

Moves.Name: Arm Thrust
Moves.Description: A quick flurry of straight-arm punches that hit two to five times.

Moves.Name: Aromatherapy
Moves.Description: A soothing scent is released to heal all status problems in the user’s party.

Moves.Name: Assist
Moves.Description: The user randomly picks and uses a move of an allied POKéMON.

Moves.Name: Astonish
Moves.Description: An attack using a startling shout. It also may make the foe flinch.

Moves.Name: Attract
Moves.Description: If it is the other gender, the foe is made infatuated and unlikely to attack.

Moves.Name: Aurora Beam
Moves.Description: A rainbow-colored attack beam. It may lower the foe’s ATTACK stat.

Moves.Name: Barrage
Moves.Description: Round objects are hurled at the foe to strike two to five times.

Moves.Name: Barrier
Moves.Description: The user creates a sturdy wall that sharply raises its DEFENSE stat.

Moves.Name: Baton Pass
Moves.Description: The user switches out, passing along any stat changes to the new battler.

Moves.Name: Beat Up
Moves.Description: All party POKéMON join in the attack. The more allies, the more damage.

Moves.Name: Belly Drum
Moves.Description: The user maximizes its ATTACK stat at the cost of half its full HP.

Moves.Name: Bide
Moves.Description: The user endures attacks for two turns, then strikes back double.

Moves.Name: Bind
Moves.Description: A long body or tentacles are used to bind the foe for two to five turns.

Moves.Name: Bite
Moves.Description: The user bites with vicious fangs. It may make the foe flinch.

Moves.Name: Blast Burn
Moves.Description: The foe is hit with a huge explosion. The user can’t move on the next turn.

Moves.Name: Blaze Kick
Moves.Description: A fiery kick with a high critical-hit ratio. It may also burn the foe.

Moves.Name: Blizzard
Moves.Description: The foe is blasted with a blizzard. It may freeze the foe solid.

Moves.Name: Block
Moves.Description: The user blocks the foe’s way with arms spread wide to prevent escape.

Moves.Name: Body Slam
Moves.Description: The user drops its full body on the foe. It may leave the foe paralyzed.

Moves.Name: Bone Club
Moves.Description: The foe is clubbed with a bone held in hand. It may make the foe flinch.

Moves.Name: Bone Rush
Moves.Description: The user strikes the foe with a bone in hand two to five times.

Moves.Name: Bonemerang
Moves.Description: The user throws a bone that hits the foe once, then once again on return.

Moves.Name: Bounce
Moves.Description: The user bounces on the foe on the 2nd turn. It may paralyze the foe.

Moves.Name: Brick Break
Moves.Description: An attack that also breaks any barrier like LIGHT SCREEN and REFLECT.

Moves.Name: Bubble
Moves.Description: A spray of bubbles hits the foe. It may lower the foe’s SPEED stat.

Moves.Name: BubbleBeam
Moves.Description: A spray of bubbles strikes the foe. It may lower the foe’s SPEED stat.

Moves.Name: Bulk Up
Moves.Description: The user bulks up its body to boost both its ATTACK and DEFENSE stats.

Moves.Name: Bullet Seed
Moves.Description: The user shoots seeds at the foe. Two to five seeds are shot at once.

Moves.Name: Bullet Seed
Moves.Description: The user shoots seeds at the foe. Two to five seeds are shot at once.

Moves.Name: Calm Mind
Moves.Description: The user focuses its mind to raise the SP. ATK and SP. DEF stats.

Moves.Name: Camouflage
Moves.Description: Alters the user’s type depending on the location’s terrain.

Moves.Name: Charge
Moves.Description: The user charges power to boost the ELECTRIC move it uses next.

Moves.Name: Charm
Moves.Description: The foe is charmed by the user’s cute appeals, sharply cutting its ATTACK.

Moves.Name: Clamp
Moves.Description: The foe is clamped and squeezed by the user’s shell for two to five turns.

Moves.Name: Comet Punch
Moves.Description: The foe is hit with a flurry of punches that strike two to five times.

Moves.Name: Confuse Ray
Moves.Description: The foe is exposed to a sinister ray that triggers confusion.

Moves.Name: Confusion
Moves.Description: A weak telekinetic attack that may also leave the foe confused.

Moves.Name: Constrict
Moves.Description: The foe is attacked with long tentacles or vines. It may lower SPEED.

Moves.Name: Conversion
Moves.Description: The user changes its type to match the type of one of its moves.

Moves.Name: Conversion 2
Moves.Description: The user changes type to make itself resistant to the last attack it took.

Moves.Name: Cosmic Power
Moves.Description: The user changes type to make itself resistant to the last attack it took.

Moves.Name: Cotton Spore
Moves.Description: Cotton-like spores cling to the foe, sharply reducing its SPEED stat.

Moves.Name: Counter
Moves.Description: A retaliation move that counters any physical hit with double the damage.

Moves.Name: Covet
Moves.Description: A cutely executed attack that also steals the foe’s hold item.

Moves.Name: Crabhammer
Moves.Description: A large pincer is used to hammer the foe. It has a high critical-hit ratio.

Moves.Name: Cross Chop
Moves.Description: The foe is hit with double chops. It has a high critical-hit ratio.

Moves.Name: Crunch
Moves.Description: The foe is crunched with sharp fangs. It may lower the foe’s SP. DEF.

Moves.Name: Crush Claw
Moves.Description: The foe is attacked with sharp claws. It may also lower the foe’s DEFENSE.

Moves.Name: Curse
Moves.Description: A move that works differently for the GHOST-type and all the other types.

Moves.Name: Cut
Moves.Description: A basic attack. It can be used to cut down thin trees and grass.

Moves.Name: Defense Curl
Moves.Description: The user curls up to conceal weak spots and raise its DEFENSE stat.

Moves.Name: Double Team
Moves.Description: The user creates illusory copies of itself to raise its evasiveness.

Moves.Name: Ember
Moves.Description: The foe is attacked with small flames. The foe may suffer a burn.

Moves.Name: Flamethrower
Moves.Description: The foe is scorched with intense flames. The foe may suffer a burn.

Moves.Name: Flash
Moves.Description: A blast of light that cuts the foe’s accuracy. It also illuminates caves.

Moves.Name: Growl
Moves.Description: The user growls in a cute way, making the foe lower its ATTACK stat.

Moves.Name: Scratch
Moves.Description: Hard, pointed, and sharp claws rake the foe.

Moves.Name: Tackle
Moves.Description: A physical attack in which the user charges, full body, into the foe.

Moves.Name: Thunderbolt
Moves.Description: A strong electrical attack that may also leave the foe paralyzed.

Moves.Name: Vine Whip
Moves.Description: The foe is struck with slender, whiplike vines.

Moves.Name: Water Gun
Moves.Description: The foe is struck with a lot of water expelled forcibly from the mouth.

Moves.Name: Waterfall
Moves.Description: The foe is struck with a lot of water expelled forcibly from the mouth.

Moves.Name: Swift
Moves.Description: The foe is struck with a lot of water expelled forcibly from the mouth.
